{"tid":910270,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李佳芯上載台慶靚相上網 好姊妹唐詩詠：Ho Leung","createTime":"2018-11-21T04:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T07:54:23.000Z","uid":82917,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2124d58048fc60199c9b7096709cf891db5eed3c","tid":910270,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"已經有2個post恥笑佢，但小美都忍唔住再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OW03r1Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOW03r1Z.png&h=e146bbcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人都鍾意喺社交網站開PO同粉絲分享佢哋嘅生活，不過過往曾經有唔少藝人因為打錯字，而淪為笑柄。之前就有坤哥將「吃好東西」寫成「吃好西」及連詩雅將「rest in peace」寫成「rest in piece」等等，今期最新「焦點」就有唐詩詠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（37）</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n無綫盛事《萬千星輝賀台慶》喺前日舉行，唔少小生花旦都盛裝出席，著得咁靚當然要影相放上網留念啦！李佳芯（Ali）喺今日凌晨時分上載自己嘅靚相上網，唔少網民都大讚佢靚，而同佢老友鬼鬼嘅唐詩詠都有留言：「Ho Leung ❤️❤️❤️😍😍」，不過詩詠似乎係唔小心將「Leng」（靚）打成「Leung」（娘），雖然只係差一隻字，但係意思就差好遠啦～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Goa69e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoa69e3.png&h=dfac7623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我姨：珍系吾巧意思嘞</span>"},{"pid":"14c9ca33118ecce4d3d343d1e774030cb5d88469","tid":910270,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"笑左 笑撚埋右"},{"pid":"23fdd7adb604928b92876c1ecdec3b94add96b98","tid":910270,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"[唐姨又發功]唐姨笑Ali好娘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/910226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/910226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n37歲唐姨公然批鬥女神Ali：好娘呀！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/909860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/909860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=